PrecisAcceptance of the transfer from the Province of Manitoba of the administration and control over two parcels of vacant land, the first being comprised of 2.35 hectares situate in the Townsite of BROCHET, and the other being comprised of 2.33 hectares situate in the Townsite of SHAMATTAWA, which are to be used by the Department of Transport as the sites for a non-directional beacons.
